    <item>
      <title>校园反战抗议者从纽约到加利福尼亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-28/campus-anti-war-protesters-dig-in-from-new-york-to-california-as-universities-and-police-take-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——从纽约到加利福尼亚州，抗议以色列与哈马斯战争的学生睡在大学校园的帐篷里，一些大学关闭了营地并逮捕了数十名示威者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-28/campus-anti-war-protesters-dig-in-from-new-york-to-california-as-universities-and-police-take-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特财政部长警告地缘政治是首要经济风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/saudi-finance-minister-says-geopolitics-world-economy-s-top-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯财政部长警告说，地缘政治可能是已经面临增长放缓和利率上升的世界经济最大的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/saudi-finance-minister-says-geopolitics-world-economy-s-top-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:38:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国间谍重磅炸弹后德国选择党失去阵地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/german-spying-far-right-party-loses-ground-after-china-revelations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲议会选举的一项新民意调查中，极右翼德国另类选择党的支持率下滑了两个百分点，这表明与中国情报部门有联系的指控正在损害该党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/german-spying-far-right-party-loses-ground-after-china-revelations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 06:54:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克拒绝在当地投票前确认选举日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/sunak-refuses-to-confirm-election-date-ahead-of-regional-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周举行的关键地区选举被视为保守党前景的风向标，英国首相拒绝在选举前确定大选日期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/sunak-refuses-to-confirm-election-date-ahead-of-regional-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国任命资本市场资深人士担任财务主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thailand-picks-capital-markets-veteran-pichai-as-finance-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 任命资本市场资深人士皮查伊·春哈瓦吉拉 (Pichai Chunhavajira) 为泰国新任财政部长，这一任命可能会缓解总理与央行之间在货币政策方面的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thailand-picks-capital-markets-veteran-pichai-as-finance-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 04:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
